140
00:09:56,492 --> 00:10:00,091
Kumohon, Ayah. Ayo kita periksa.

141
00:10:00,092 --> 00:10:01,292
Aku?

142
00:10:05,092 --> 00:10:07,991
Aku tidak mengerti mengapa dia begitu takut.

143
00:10:07,992 --> 00:10:11,991
Tidak ada boneka kertas di sini.

144
00:10:11,992 --> 00:10:13,891
Benar, lihat?

145
00:10:13,892 --> 00:10:15,491
Benar.

