214
00:14:22,807 --> 00:14:25,407
Kalian akan mandi sekarang?

215
00:14:26,407 --> 00:14:28,306
Kau sudah selesai mandi, Ny. Akechi?

216
00:14:28,307 --> 00:14:30,706
Ya. Merasa sedikit kedinginan.

217
00:14:30,707 --> 00:14:33,706
Kalau begitu, bagaimana kalau kita pergi minum bersama?

218
00:14:33,707 --> 00:14:37,607
Maaf. Aku masih punya pekerjaan.

219
00:14:38,807 --> 00:14:40,407
Baiklah, sampai nanti!

220
00:14:42,207 --> 00:14:44,306
